== 觀光資源 ==

{{Tsl|ja|五条川|五條川}}沿岸區域為[[日本櫻名所100選|日本櫻名所100選]]之一，在岩倉市內區域就約有1,400顆[[櫻花樹|櫻花樹]]，每年春天在此區域會舉辦岩倉櫻花祭。<ref>{{Cite web| url=https://www.city.iwakura.aichi.jp/0000000348.html| title=見どころ| date=2016-11-30| publisher=岩倉市政府| language=ja| accessdate=2021-12-02| archive-date=2022-05-03| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503051920/https://www.city.iwakura.aichi.jp/0000000348.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web| url=https://hanami.walkerplus.com/detail/ar0623e26078/| title=岩倉五条川の桜| work=Walker+| language=ja| accessdate=2021-12-02| archive-date=2022-05-03| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503051922/https://hanami.walkerplus.com/detail/ar0623e26078/}}</ref>

八月上旬岩倉市內的神社會共同舉辦山車夏季，共有三台山車會在岩倉市內遊行。<ref>{{Cite web| url=https://www.dashi-aichi.jp/festivals/detail/29/| title=岩倉市山車夏まつり| publisher=あいち山車まつり日本一協議会| language=ja| accessdate=2021-12-02| archive-date=2021-12-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211202021302/https://www.dashi-aichi.jp/festivals/detail/29/}}</ref>

